		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Any Lisp programmers here? I recently encountered it at work, and was very impressed with what a co-worker of mine did with it. I'm fascinated by its apparent underdog status, because there seem to be so many accounts of software teams delivering a project on time, under budget and with a small number of people. So, I'm learning it now. Of course, my nes game is still top priority until I finish it, but I'll be learning Lisp on the side.

		

